window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Set against the colorful tumult of events that gave rise to our fledgling nation, this novel of romance and adventure introduces Phillipe Charboneau. </p> <p>The illegitimate son of an English nobleman, Phillipe flees Europe and, as Philip Kent, joins the men who set our course for freedom. </p> <p><i>The Bastard</i> is the first volume in the Kent Family Chronicles, a series of novels that details one family's journey in the early years of the American nation.</p>"; 
